<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN320-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. vīrai veḷiyaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN320">
      <lg type="edition" style="pūṭṭuvil">
<l>muṉṟiṉ muññaiyoṭu mucuṇṭai pampip</l>
<l>pantar vēṇṭāp palartūṅku nīḻaṟ</l>
<l>kaimmāṉ vēṭṭuvaṉ kaṉaituyiṉ maṭinteṉap</l>
<l>pārvai maṭappiṇai taḻīip piṟitōr</l>
<l>tīrtoḻiṟ ṟaṉikkalai tiḷaittuviḷai yāṭa</l>
<l>viṉpuṟu puṇarnilai kaṇṭa maṉaiyōḷ</l>
<l>kaṇava ṉeḻutalu mañcik kalaiyē</l>
<l>piṇaivayiṟ ṟīrtalu mañci yāvatu</l>
<l>milvaḻaṅ kāmaiyiṟ kalleṉa volittu</l>
<l>māṉataṭ peyta vuṇaṅkutiṉai valci</l>
<l>kāṉak kōḻiyō  ṭitalkavarn  tuṇṭeṉa</l>
<l>vāra neruppi ṉāra ṉāṟat</l>
<l>taṭivārn tiṭṭa muḻuvaḷ ḷūra</l>
<l>mirumpē rokkalo ṭoruṅkiṉi taruntit</l>
<l>taṅkiṉai ceṉmō pāṇa taṅkātu</l>
<l>vēntutaru viḻukkūḻ paricilark keṉṟu</l>
<l>marukā tīyum vaṇmai</l>
<l>yuraicā ṉeṭuntakai yōmpu mūrē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Because, in the front yard, as bindweed and Muññai are growing thickly,</l>
<l>in the shade in which many sleep who do not need an arbour</l>
<l>the elephant hunter has dropped into deep sleep,</l>
<l>while, embracing the youthful decoy doe, one other </l>
<l>solitary stag whose work had ended was sporting [and] playing,</l>
<l>the woman of the house who saw [them] in blissful union,</l>
<l>afraid that [her] husband would get up and afraid</l>
<l>that the stag would find [its] end by the side of the doe,</l>
<l>because it was not moving at all, made loud noise</l>
<l>[and] because the food of drying millet poured on the deer skin</l>
<l>had been seized [and] eaten the the wild fowl and partridge,</l>
<l>seasoned Āral fish with a fire of sandal wood:</l>
<l>“stay here, </l>
<l>eating sweetly together with [your] famous kinfolk</l>
<l>from the whole meat that has been cut into pieces,</l>
<l>  [and then] go, bard, without staying</l>
<l>in the village protected by the paragon worthy to be spoken of,</l>
<l>of a generosity that always gives without </l>
<l>stinting to solicitors the excellent food given by the king.   </l>
</lg>
    </div>
